  <text>
    <body>
      <div type="account" ana="bk:account">
        <head>Empfang Gelt
Neuer Empfang
Admodiations Gelt</head>
        <p>Die ertragnis des stypatirten Admodiationsquarti von <date when="1718-04-23" confidence="medium" resp="#machine">Georgi 1718</date> bis <date when="1719" confidence="medium" resp="#machine">1719</date> per <measure ana="bk:money" unit="fl" quantity="6200" confidence="high" resp="#machine">6200 fl</measure> haben die herrschaftl. Admodiatores, als <persName confidence="high" resp="#machine">Peter Walser</persName>, alter <name type="role" confidence="high" resp="#machine">Landtammann</name>, dessen Söhne <persName confidence="high" resp="#machine">Thomas</persName> und <persName confidence="high" resp="#machine">Anthoni Walser</persName>, <persName confidence="high" resp="#machine">Florian Wolf</persName> sel. gewester hochfürstlicher <name type="role" confidence="high" resp="#machine">Weingartenmeister</name> nachfolgender gestalt abgestattet. Und zwar mit bahrem Gelt zu Handen der fürstl. Verwaltung vom <date when="1718-09-01" confidence="high" resp="#machine">1. September 1718</date> bis <date when="1720-03-31" confidence="medium" resp="#machine">Endt Marty 1720</date> zusammen hiedurch geliefert per <measure ana="bk:money" unit="fl" quantity="513" confidence="high" resp="#machine">513 fl</measure></p>
      </div>
      <div type="account" ana="bk:account">
        <head>Von dem <name type="role" confidence="high" resp="#machine">Haupt Zollner</name> <placeName confidence="high" resp="#machine">Liechtenstein</placeName> <persName confidence="high" resp="#machine">Thomas Walser</persName></head>
        <p>Von <date when="1718-10-01" confidence="medium" resp="#machine">1. und respective 22 Octobris</date> bis <date when="1718-11-22" confidence="medium" resp="#machine">22 Novembris 1718</date> <measure ana="bk:money" unit="fl" quantity="48" confidence="high" resp="#machine">48 fl</measure> <measure ana="bk:money" unit="kr" quantity="25" confidence="high" resp="#machine">25 kr</measure></p>
        <p>Von <date when="1718-11-22" confidence="medium" resp="#machine">22 Novembris</date> bis <date when="1718-12-22" confidence="medium" resp="#machine">22 Decembris</date> <measure ana="bk:money" unit="fl" quantity="60" confidence="high" resp="#machine">60 fl</measure> <measure ana="bk:money" unit="kr" quantity="15" confidence="high" resp="#machine">15 kr</measure></p>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
